## 2. Sequence Diagram (Message Flow)

```plantuml
@startuml
title Message Flow - AUTO_JOIN Event

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

participant "Class-Control\nApplication" as CC #Orange
participant "Redis Stream\n(CLASSROOM_EVENTS)" as Redis #Salmon
participant "Pod 1\n(device-control)" as P1 #LightGreen
participant "Pod 2\n(device-control)" as P2 #LightGreen
participant "Pod 3\n(device-control)" as P3 #LightGreen
participant "Student s1\n(on Pod 1)" as S1 #LightBlue
participant "Student s7\n(on Pod 2)" as S7 #LightBlue

== Event Publishing ==

CC -> Redis : XADD classroom_events * payload\n{\n  "eventType": "AUTO_JOIN",\n  "studentIds": ["s1", "s7"],\n  "classId": "ee78ccf3-..."\n}

== Fan-Out to All Pods ==

Redis -> P1 : Deliver event\n(studentIds: [s1, s7])
Redis -> P2 : Deliver event\n(studentIds: [s1, s7])
Redis -> P3 : Deliver event\n(studentIds: [s1, s7])

== Pod 1 Processing ==

P1 -> P1 : Check activeSessions\nfor "s1"
note right of P1 : s1 FOUND ✅
P1 -> S1 : Send WebSocket\nMessage (AUTO_JOIN)

P1 -> P1 : Check activeSessions\nfor "s7"
note right of P1 : s7 NOT FOUND ❌\nSkip

== Pod 2 Processing ==

P2 -> P2 : Check activeSessions\nfor "s1"
note right of P2 : s1 NOT FOUND ❌\nSkip

P2 -> P2 : Check activeSessions\nfor "s7"
note right of P2 : s7 FOUND ✅
P2 -> S7 : Send WebSocket\nMessage (AUTO_JOIN)

== Pod 3 Processing ==

P3 -> P3 : Check activeSessions\nfor "s1"
note right of P3 : s1 NOT FOUND ❌\nSkip

P3 -> P3 : Check activeSessions\nfor "s7"
note right of P3 : s7 NOT FOUND ❌\nSkip

@enduml
```

