## 4. Activity Diagram (Pod Consumer Logic)

```plantuml
@startuml
title Pod Consumer - Event Processing Logic

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

start

:Receive event from\nRedis Stream\n(CLASSROOM_EVENTS);

:Parse event payload;

:Extract **studentIds[]**\nfrom event;

while (More studentIds\nto process?) is (Yes)
    :Get next **studentId**;

    if (studentId exists in\n**activeSessions** map?) then (Yes)
        :Get **WebSocketSession**\nfrom map;

        if (Session is **open**?) then (Yes)
            :Send WebSocket\nmessage to student;
            #LightGreen :Message Delivered ✅;
        else (No)
            :Remove stale session\nfrom activeSessions;
            #Salmon :Session Closed ❌;
        endif

    else (No)
        #LightYellow :Student not on\nthis pod → Skip;
    endif

endwhile (No)

:Acknowledge message\nin Redis Stream;

stop

@enduml
```

