## How to Render

You can render these diagrams using:

| Tool | URL |
|------|-----|
| **PlantUML Online** | [www.plantuml.com/plantuml](http://www.plantuml.com/plantuml) |
| **VS Code Extension** | PlantUML plugin by jebbs |
| **IntelliJ Plugin** | PlantUML Integration |
| **CLI** | `java -jar plantuml.jar diagram.puml` |

Copy any `@startuml ... @enduml` block into the tool to generate the visual diagram.